  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal-400 mb-6">What is Shockwave Therapy?</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-6">
    <span class="font-semibold text-teal-300">Shockwave Therapy</span> is a non-invasive treatment that uses high-energy sound waves to stimulate healing in painful muscles, tendons, and joints. It helps break up scar tissue, increase blood flow, and kickstart your body’s natural repair process. There are no needles, no medications—just sound waves working with your body.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">How Does Shockwave Therapy Work?</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mb-8 space-y-2">
    <li>Sound waves are delivered directly to the injured area.</li>
    <li>These waves trigger micro-healing, boost circulation, and reduce chronic inflammation.</li>
    <li>Your body responds by accelerating tissue repair, breaking up calcifications, and reducing pain.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-6">Radial vs Focused Shockwave—What’s the Difference?</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 mb-12">
    <!-- Radial -->
    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl flex-1 shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-4">Radial Shockwave (RSWT)</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 text-gray-300 space-y-2">
        <li>Sound waves spread out like ripples from a stone in water.</li>
        <li>Treats larger, more superficial areas (like muscle knots or tendons near the surface).</li>
        <li>Best for mild-to-moderate conditions or muscle tension.</li>
        <li>Great for general pain relief and tissue “wake up.”</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Focused -->
    <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-teal-500 p-6 rounded-2xl flex-1 shadow-xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-300 mb-4">Focused Shockwave (FSWT)</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Sound waves are concentrated into a single, deeper point.</li>
        <li>Reaches tissues other treatments can’t—great for chronic, deep, or stubborn injuries.</li>
        <li>More precise and can target pain at its true source.</li>
        <li>Backed by strong research for lasting pain relief and tissue regeneration.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="bg-teal-800/30 p-4 rounded-xl text-sm text-white">
        <strong class="text-teal-200">Why Choose Focused Shockwave?</strong><br>
        If your pain has lasted a long time, isn’t getting better with other treatments, or is deep beneath the surface, Focused Shockwave offers the most advanced, evidence-based results.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Is Shockwave Right for Me?</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-200 mb-6">
    Shockwave is a proven option for issues like plantar fasciitis, Achilles tendinopathy, tennis elbow, calcific tendonitis, and other stubborn muscle or tendon pain. Every plan is tailored—with the right type of shockwave and the right dose—based on your specific needs.
  </p>

